==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kind-hearted
<hw>Kind"-heart`ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having kindness
of nature; sympathetic; characterized by a humane disposition; <as>as, a
<ex>kind-hearted</ex> landlord</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>To thy self at least <qex>kind-hearted</qex> prove.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Kind-heartedness</ent>⟦br⟧
